3418:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Computation is using temperature sensor calibration values
3419:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         stored in system memory for each device during production.
3420:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Calculation formula:
3421:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           Temperature = ((TS_ADC_DATA - TS_CAL1)
3422:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                           * (TS_CAL2_TEMP - TS_CAL1_TEMP))
3423:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                         / (TS_CAL2 - TS_CAL1) + TS_CAL1_TEMP
3424:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           with TS_ADC_DATA = temperature sensor raw data measured by ADC
3425:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                Avg_Slope = (TS_CAL2 - TS_CAL1)
