5049:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         fully configurable: sequencer length and each rank
5050:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         affectation to a channel are configurable.
5051:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to description of function @ref LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerLength().
