5053:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Refer to device datasheet for channels availability.
5054:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Usage of the returned channel number:
5055:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - To reinject this channel into another function LL_ADC_xxx:
5056:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           the returned channel number is only partly formatted on definition
5057:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           of literals LL_ADC_CHANNEL_x. Therefore, it has to be compared
5058:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           with parts of literals LL_ADC_CHANNEL_x or using
