5160:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC continuous conversion mode on ADC group regular.
5161:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Description of ADC continuous conversion mode:
5162:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - single mode: one conversion per trigger
5163:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - continuous mode: after the first trigger, following
5164:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           conversions launched successively automatically.
5165:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   It is not possible to enable both ADC group regular
5166:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         continuous mode and sequencer discontinuous mode.
5167:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On this STM32 series, setting of this feature is conditioned to
5168:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC state:
5169:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         ADC must be disabled or enabled without conversion on going
5170:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         on group regular.
5171:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @rmtoll CFGR     CONT           LL_ADC_REG_SetContinuousMode
5172:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @param  ADCx ADC instance
5173:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @param  Continuous This parameter can be one of the following values:
5174:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @arg @ref LL_ADC_REG_CONV_SINGLE
5175:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         @arg @ref LL_ADC_REG_CONV_CONTINUOUS
5176:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @retval None
5177:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   */
5178:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h **** __STATIC_INLINE void LL_ADC_REG_SetContinuousMode(ADC_TypeDef *ADCx, uint32_t Continuous)
5179:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h **** {
