1126:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c **** /**
1127:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @brief  Get ADC injected group conversion result.
1128:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @note   Reading register JDRx automatically clears ADC flag JEOC
1129:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         (ADC group injected end of unitary conversion).
1130:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @note   This function does not clear ADC flag JEOS
1131:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         (ADC group injected end of sequence conversion)
1132:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         Occurrence of flag JEOS rising:
1133:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *          - If sequencer is composed of 1 rank, flag JEOS is equivalent
1134:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *            to flag JEOC.
1135:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *          - If sequencer is composed of several ranks, during the scan
1136:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *            sequence flag JEOC only is raised, at the end of the scan sequence
1137:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *            both flags JEOC and EOS are raised.
1138:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         Flag JEOS must not be cleared by this function because
1139:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         it would not be compliant with low power features
1140:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         (feature low power auto-wait, not available on all STM32 series).
1141:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         To clear this flag, either use function:
1142:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         in programming model IT: @ref HAL_ADC_IRQHandler(), in programming
1143:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         model polling: @ref HAL_ADCEx_InjectedPollForConversion()
1144:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *         or @ref __HAL_ADC_CLEAR_FLAG(&hadc, ADC_FLAG_JEOS).
1145:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @param hadc ADC handle
1146:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @param InjectedRank the converted ADC injected rank.
1147:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *          This parameter can be one of the following values:
1148:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *            @arg @ref ADC_INJECTED_RANK_1 ADC group injected rank 1
1149:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *            @arg @ref ADC_INJECTED_RANK_2 ADC group injected rank 2
1150:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *            @arg @ref ADC_INJECTED_RANK_3 ADC group injected rank 3
1151:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   *            @arg @ref ADC_INJECTED_RANK_4 ADC group injected rank 4
1152:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @retval ADC group injected conversion data
1153:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   */
